column1: Data as of: Wednesday, March 15, 2023, version: 2023031506

The number of presentations (visits) to this hospital’s emergency department. 
Data are shown for total presentations, and by the urgency of the patient’s need for care (their triage category), as assessed by a healthcare professional in the emergency department.

Note: The measure includes presentations with any type of visit code (not just emergency presentations).

column4: Triage 1. Resuscitation (requires immediate treatment, which was defined for this report as commencement of clinical care within 2 minutes from presentation time)
